## 1. ARCHITECTURE PHILOSOPHY

The Human Empowerment Hub is a dedicated sub-application within the main provider dashboard. It is **not** a monolith. It is composed of highly modular, reusable components spread across multiple routes to prevent bloat and maintain a clean UX.

The core principle: **Ascension over Automation.** The UI must gamify trust in the AI, moving the user through distinct levels of operational capability.

